   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,954:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,955:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: What is TMS?
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,956:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: TMS (Telemedicine Management System)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,977:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  is a full-stack digital healthcare platform that enables remote medical
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: consultations between patients and doctors. It provides a complete end-to-end telemedicine workflow — from
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: AI-powered symptom triage to video consultations, e-prescriptions, real-time Bluetooth vitals monitoring, and
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: secure payment processing.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Key Highlights
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Feature | Description |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |---------|-------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:58,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: AI Triage Chatbot
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,009:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Google Gemini AI-powered symptom assessment
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with 4-tier urgency classification and emergency detection |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Video Consultations
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Real-time peer-to-peer
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: video/audio calls using WebRTC with WebSocket signaling |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: e-Prescriptions
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,010:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Digital prescriptions with
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,022:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: auto-generated PDF (ReportLab) including QR codes for verification |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,022:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,024:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,024:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Bluetooth Vitals
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Web Bluetooth API for
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pairing IoT health devices (heart rate, SpO2, BP, temperature) |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Multi-Role Portal
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Separate dashboards for
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Patients, Doctors, and Admins with role-based access control |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Payment Processing
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Integrated payment system
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with UPI/Card support and transaction verification |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,041:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,041:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,042:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Medical Records
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Secure file upload and storage for lab
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: reports, scans, and medical documents |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Real-time Communication
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | WebSocket-based real-time chat, vitals
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: streaming, and prescription updates during consultations |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Who Uses It?
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Role | Access |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |------|--------|
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Patient
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,058:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Register, triage chat, browse doctors, book appointments, pay, join video
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: call, view prescriptions 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  records |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Doctor
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Login, manage schedule, join consultations, write/upload
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: prescriptions, manage medicine templates, view earnings |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Admin
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Platform analytics, manage all doctors/patients,
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: view revenue, monitor appointments |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 2. PROBLEM STATEMENT
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,072:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: In many regions, especially rural and semi-urban areas, patients face significant challenges in accessing quality
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,074:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: healthcare:
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,074:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,075:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Geographic barriers
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Patients must travel long distances to see specialists
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Long wait times
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — OPD queues can take hours, especially in public hospitals
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Paper-based records
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Prescriptions get lost; medical history is fragmented
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: No triage guidance
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Patients don
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: t know whether their symptoms need emergency care, urgent care,
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: or routine visits
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Device silos
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Wearable health data isn
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,076:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: t connected to the consultation workflow
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,090:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,091:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Payment friction
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Complex billing processes and lack of digital payment options
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: TMS solves all of these problems
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  by providing a unified digital platform for remote healthcare delivery.
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3. OBJECTIVES
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Enable Remote Consultations
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Allow patients to consult doctors via video from anywhere
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: AI-Powered Triage
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Help patients assess symptom urgency before booking appointments
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Digital Prescriptions
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Replace paper prescriptions with verifiable digital e-Prescriptions
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: IoT Health Integration
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Connect Bluetooth health devices for real-time vitals monitoring
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  5 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,093:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Streamlined Payments
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,107:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Provide seamless digital payment for consultations
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,108:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  6 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Centralized Medical Records
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Give patients a single platform to store and access all medical
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: documents
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  7 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Admin Oversight
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Provide hospital administrators with analytics and management tools
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 4. TECH STACK
