   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Adds CORS middleware
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  allowing all origins for development
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Creates all database tables
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  via 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Base.metadata.create_all()
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Creates upload directories
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,872:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  for prescriptions, records, and profiles
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,872:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  5 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,874:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Mounts static file serving
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  for uploaded files at 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: /uploads
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  6 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Registers all 11 API routers
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  plus WebSocket router
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  7 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Serves the frontend
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  from the project root (HTML, CSS, JS)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  8 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Auto-seeds the database
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  on first startup if empty
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  9 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Auto-migrates
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  prescriptions table (adds 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: image_path
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:26:59,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  column if missing)
