   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Extension whitelist + 10MB size limit |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 11. AI TRIAGE CHATBOT
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Overview
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The AI Triage Chatbot is the most complex feature (699 lines). It uses a 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: hybrid dual-engine architecture
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Red Flag Safety Layer
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  (always runs first) — Hard-coded regex patterns for life-threatening
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: emergencies
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Google Gemini AI
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  (primary) — Conversational AI using Gemini 2.0 Flash model
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Rule-Based Fallback
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  (secondary) — OPQRST-based symptom scoring engine
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Red Flag Detection (Hard-Coded Safety)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The safety layer scans EVERY message for emergency keywords BEFORE any AI processing:
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Category | Trigger Patterns | Response |
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |----------|-----------------|----------|
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Chest Pain
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: chest pain
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , 
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: chest
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pressure
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
