   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Rule-Based Fallback Engine
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: When Gemini is unavailable, the system falls back to a structured OPQRST conversation:
