   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Headache (score: 3), Migraine (4), Fever (3), High fever (5)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Cough (2), Sore throat (2), Nausea (2), Vomiting (3)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,943:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Abdominal pain (4), Back pain (3), Dizziness (3)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,944:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,945:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Shortness of breath (4), Palpitations (4), etc.
