   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,949:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — Listen to initial complaint, identify symptoms
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:00,950:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
