   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,575:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │    POST /api/prescriptions/create
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,575:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │    → Creates Rx + links medicines
