   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 15. PAYMENT SYSTEM
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Payment Flow
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Patient books appointment
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         ▼
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Appointment created (status: pending, payment: pending)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         ▼
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Patient clicks "Pay" → selects method (UPI/Card/NetBanking)
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         ▼
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     POST /api/payments/create
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     {appointment_id, amount, payment_method}
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         ▼
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,622:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Payment Service:
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,622:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     ├── Generate transaction_id: "TMS{date}{uuid}"
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,624:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     ├── Create Payment record (status: "success")
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     ├── Update Appointment: payment_status → "paid"
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     └── Update Appointment: status → "confirmed"
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         │
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         ▼
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     Return: {id, amount, transaction_id, status}
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Note
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Currently uses a mock payment gateway that always succeeds. For production, integrate with Razorpay,
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:01,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Stripe, or similar.
