   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,844:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,844:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: In summary, TMS is a comprehensive telemedicine platform that brings together AI, real-time
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: communication, IoT integration, and digital health workflows into one cohesive system. It
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,859:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,876:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s built
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,915:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with modern technologies, follows best practices in security and architecture, and is designed to
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,926:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: scale. The platform is fully functional today with 42 API endpoints, real-time WebSocket
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,926:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: communication, AI-powered triage, video consultations, digital prescriptions with QR verification,
   DEBUG: 2026-05-31 21:27:02,942:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: and Bluetooth health device integration. Thank you for your attention. I
